每个平台上的网页唯一
数据库设计
    #专门为站点信息保存分配一个数据库
    #为每一个站点分配一个表
    sites:
    htmlinfo:
        docID   url     title       date
    htmlsource:
        docID   source  parsedsource
    #htmlinfo and htmlsource is one-to-one conresponding
-----------------------------------------------------------
    imginfo:
        imgID   docID   imgUrl
    imgsource:
        imgID   source
    #imginfo and imgsource is one-to-one coresponding

Format of config information:
    home_url:
        siteID, url
    
Format of each Site:
    siteID (Name of Database)
        tables:
            htmlinfo
            htmlsource
            imginfo
            imgsource

            

        
        
